S.FORM: Norway u Norway sa i labu nu Europe (O-Cuo 歐洲), itiza i 62 00 N, 10 00 E. u ahebal nu lala' mapulung sa izaw ku 323,802 km2. u ahebal nu lala'ay sa izaw ku 304,282 km2, u ahebal nu nanumay sa izaw ku 19,520 km2. hamin nu tademawan sa 5,594,34 (2025). kakalukan umah sa 2.70%, kilakilangan umah sa 27.80%, zumaay henay umah sa 69.50%. tapang tusu nu kanatal u tapang tusu nu kanatal sa u Oslo . kakinginan nu kanatal demiad kakinging nu kanatal demiad sa 17 bulad 5 demiad. tabakiay a tapang nu kanatal u tabakiay a tapang nu kanatal (cong-tung, 總統) ayza sa ci Harald V, micakat a demiad sa i 1991 a mihca 1 bulad 17 demiad. cunli u cunli nu Norway ayza sa ci Jonas Gahr Støre (Ap) (2021–), micakat a demiad sa i 2021 a mihcaan 10 bulad 14 demiad. likisi atu lalangawan nu Norway namakayda i amis nu Ze-Er-Man a tademaw kunyun pitu a lasubu siwa a bataan (790) a mihecaan malingatu misaahebal, katukuh i cacay a malebut enem a bataan idaw ku enem (1066) a mihecaan Denmark (Dan-May 丹麥) a tademaw nu iluc madebung nuheni ku Ing-Ke-Lan , pangangan han tu "Wey-Cin-se-day" , u O-Cuo nanu mukasiay a zida' katukuh i nutebanay a se-ci nu milakuuytay a zitay. . Vikings (Wey-Cin a tademaw 維京人) sasi nganganay a pacunaay tu balunga a tademaw, itda kuhuheni i De-Lan luyaluy a subal , Fa-Luo luyaluy a subal , Iceland (Pin-Daw 冰島), Greenland (Ke-Lin-Lan 格陵蘭), patideng kunuheni tu kakitidaan, itini i pulu' a bataan nu nikudan a secian cacay henay kasiwantan kueneng i Mey-Cuo Niw-Fen-Lan a siluma' sa. . unuheni han u micebisay nu kukung, palecad han kunipisiwbay, patideng kunuheni tu luma i Europe (O-Cuo 歐洲) nu lilis a dadipasan atu tepal nu sauwacan. idaw kuni pikilukan sakamusa i kunyun walu a lasubu tulu a bataan idaw ku siwa (839) a mihcaan namidebung henay ku nuheni tu Byzantinum hungtiay a kanatal (Pay-Can-Tin-Di'-Kuo 拜占廷帝國) micaliw tu hiday mamisawacu Africa . . nuheni a tademaw laklak sa i Europe (O-Cuo 歐洲), maala tu England a Denmark nu niyadu', Gi-Fu-Luo-Se , France a Nuo-Man-Di . katukuh tu Wey-Cin-Se-Day a hedek, Pey-O culal sa masacacay micidek patideng tu kanatal atu kuo-wan , milayap kunuheni tu kelistukiw , nikudan katukuh sabaw tu enem (16) a seci nu lingatu namaka Denmark , Sweden atu Norway misakaputay nu Se-Kan a Na-Wey-Ya kanatalay a lanmun . cacay a malebut tulu a lasubu siwa a bataan idaw ku pitu (1397) a mihcaan enem a bulad sabaw tu pitu a demiad, Denmark , Sweden atu Norway dayhuw itini i Sweden timulan a tukay Ka-Er-Ma mikaygi, pakasimata ku nuheni tu tuluay a wankuo mapulung kunuheni palekal tu Denmark nI-wang ci Ma-Ke-Li-Te' ise u kuo-wan atu secen a tademaw, u Norway atu Sweden kuowan u Denmark kuowan ku sikawaway . . Denmark wan-se mala nu tatuluay a kanatal mikuwanay.taya nu Sweden atu Norway hidantu ku wankuo caay bulici nuheni ku ngangan. . Denmark wanse pulungen nuheni ku tuluay a sakayputah a cabay atu nu hitay a kakawaw , sisa Sweden atu Norway hidantu ku wankuo caay bulici nuheni ku ngangan. . Denmark wanse pulungen nuheni ku tuluay a sakayputah a cabay atu nu hitay a kakawaw , nu kanatal tu akawaw u kanatal tu kumicidekay amasacacay. 但是, . nika , inika pulunga tawya, Denmark kuowan caay kawni pikawaw tu Sweden secen atu kuowan, nu Sweden kuo-wan sakawaluay a Ka-Er mikuwan henay sa. . itini i salaadan sa, Sweden nu tateneng mikuwan sa numaka i nuudip tu a kanatal nu siilaya ani singkiwan nu secen tatapang 攝政官. . tuluay a lanman hamin han ku Europe a kakitidaan pulung han tu cacay a wankuo amikuwan, pangalep tu Pa-o a niyaduan palung hantu cacaya a kuowan amikuwan, paka siida tu Pa-o a kanatal paculi tu De-I'-Ce-Han-Sa tungmum itida i Po-Luo-Di' a bayu atu amis a bayu anipisiwbaya putuna ku sakatayni. sabaw tu lima (15) a seci mahedek, Denmark wanse atu Sweden siidaay nai ku watan nikasasukapah, mihantaya a lanman sawsawni masasu ada kunuheni . . Ke-Li-S-Di-An e'se, i cacay a malebut lima a lasubu tusa a bataan (1520) a mihcaan ladayen nida ku hitay mialaw tu Sweden mihantaya nu mikuwanay a Sweden suodu S-De-Ke-E-Muo , sisa pipatayen nuheni ku katuuday nu palekalay tu kawaw a Sweden nusi idaay. 16 . sabaw tu enem a (16) a seci nu aayaw a Ka-Ma-Lenmum mililitay a tademaw cacay a malebut tulu a lasubu walu a bataan (1380) a mihcaan ci Ma-Ke-Li-Te' ise pabelien nida ku teluc, Po-Ma-La-Ni-Ia a pala Ay-Li-Ke'-Zn Norway kiowan. . u Norway han naw Di-Ke-Lin-Lan subal , Iceland atu Fa-luo luyaluy a subal namakayni malingatu u Denmark kumi kuwanay. . pulung nu lanmun sayaway, Ma-ke-li-te' ese a dawmi' nu wayway u Denmark wanse madiput nu pinaay a kanatal nu namuh, sisa nikudan satu Denmark wanse caay tu pisengal mikuwan tu Norway atu Sweden a labuay nu kawaw, nikahida sisa lanman miliyas tu nuhenian. 14至16世紀, . sabaw tu sepat (14) katukuh sabaw tu enem (16) a seci , Denmark maydih misungay tu Han-Sa' Tung-Mung milihida tu Puo-Luo-Di' a bayu a mikawaw pa'pun malihida malepacaw. . Denmark Aw-ten-paw wancaw a Ke'-Li-S-Di'-An ese'maala nida ku De-I-Ce a kitidaan Se-Le-Su-I-Ke atu He-E-Se-Tay-In a sapikuwan. 1521 . cacay a malebut lima a bataan tusa a lasubu idaw ku cacay (1521) a mihcaan Sweden siidaay ci Ku-S-Ta-Hu .Wa-Sa' itida i Da-La-Na-Sen milingatu palekal tu baluhay a Denmark nu hidayan. 1523年, . cacay a malebut lima a lasubu tusa a bataan idaw ku tulu (1523) a mihcaan ci Ku-Se-Ta-Hu .Wa-Sa' itida i Han-Sa- Tunmum nipadangan sa midebung tu Se-De-Ke-E-Muo , Denmark ahitayan mademec, Sweden mapalekal misatada'. . mapatideng satu ku Sweden , Ka-E-Ma-Lanmum mabulesak tu kunuheni, nika u Denmark atu Norway mahidatu kunuheni masasukapah a kanatal. cacay a malebut lima a lasubu tulu a bataan idaw ku sepat (1534) a mihcaan Norway mapalawpes ku wankuo a ngangan, pahetiken mala Denmark a kenis. 17 . sabaw tu pitu (17) a seci, Sweden mangalay mialaw tu Po-Luo-Di' a bayu caay pisengal atu Denmark malepacaw. cacay a malebut enem a lasubu lima a bataan idaw ku walu (1658) a mihcaan, Sweden sadikuday satu maalaw tu nuheni ku S-Kan-De-Na-Wia-ya a kumay s nu hatidaay tu nutenes ani a lawan nu Denmark a nutimulan nu dadipasan a kakitidaan. 1809年, . cacay a malebut walu a lasubu idaw ku siwa (1809) a mihcaan, E'-Russia dikuo debungan nu Sweden mikuwan tu Finland . Na-Puo-Lun nikaminan satu malepacaw , sakamusa cacay a malebut walu a lasubu cacay a bataan idaw ku sepat (1814) a mihcaan nu Ci-E nika sasulitan nika sasulitan, Denmark hiyan nu Norway sipabeli i Sweden . apuyu kuni kalpacaw amiwaies, Norway mala Sweden kuowan nikuwanan a wankuo. 1905年, . cacay a malebut siwa a lasubu idaw ku lima (1905) a mihcaan, Norway han misadawmin tu wayway namaka Sweden micidek masacacay. 1938年, . cacay a malebut siwa a lasubu tulu a bataan idaw ku walu (1938) a mihcaan , Iceland miales tu Denmark micidek masacacay.
